@startuml Bus_Interaction
title EmuAVR - Bus Communication Diagram

actor CPU
participant Bus
participant SRAM
participant Port
participant UART

CPU ->> Bus: write(0x0025, 0xFF)
activate Bus
Bus ->> Port: write(0x05, 0xFF)
activate Port
Port ->> Port: Update PORT register
Port -->> Bus
deactivate Port
Bus -->> CPU
deactivate Bus

CPU ->> Bus: read(0x0100)
activate Bus
Bus ->> SRAM: read(0x00A0)
activate SRAM
SRAM -->> Bus: 0x42
deactivate SRAM
Bus -->> CPU: 0x42
deactivate Bus

CPU ->> Bus: write(0x00C0, 0x55)
activate Bus
Bus ->> UART: write(0x00, 0x55)
activate UART
UART ->> UART: Update data register
UART ->> UART: Emit output character
UART -->> Bus
deactivate UART
Bus -->> CPU
deactivate Bus

@enduml
